          "nodeSize": "large",
          "id": "test-strategy",
          "on": {
            "ready": {
              "action": "goto",
              "target": "traceability"
            },
            "approved": {
              "action": "terminate",
              "status": "blocked"
            },
            "changes-requested": {
              "action": "terminate",
              "status": "blocked"
            },
            "needs_input": {
              "action": "goto",
              "target": "source-decision-gate",
              "input": "signal"
            },
            "blocked": {
              "action": "terminate",
              "status": "blocked"
            },
            "failed": {
              "action": "retry",
              "policy": {
                "maxAttempts": 1,
                "onExhausted": {
                  "action": "terminate",
                  "status": "failed"
                },
                "when": {
                  "failureClassification": "transient"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "type": "agent",
          "agentId": "architecture-agent"
        },
        {
          "description": "Rakenna source → artifact → acceptance → test -ketju `.ballet/outputs/traceability-manifest.yaml`:iin ja jätä todellinen uncovered coverage näkyväksi.",
          "nodeStyle": "sol",
          "nodeSize": "large",
          "id": "traceability",
          "on": {
            "ready": {
              "action": "goto",
              "target": "independent-blueprint-verifier"
            },
            "approved": {
              "action": "terminate",
              "status": "blocked"
            },
            "changes-requested": {
              "action": "terminate",
              "status": "blocked"
            },
            "needs_input": {
              "action": "goto",
              "target": "source-decision-gate",
              "input": "signal"
            },
            "blocked": {
              "action": "terminate",
              "status": "blocked"
            },
            "failed": {
              "action": "retry",
              "policy": {
                "maxAttempts": 1,
                "onExhausted": {
                  "action": "terminate",
                  "status": "failed"
                },
                "when": {
                  "failureClassification": "transient"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "type": "agent",
          "agentId": "roadmap-agent"
        },
        {
          "description": "Tarkista kaikki lähteet ja artifactit suoraan levyltä riippumattomana kirjoittajista. Kirjoita `.ballet/outputs/blueprint-review.yaml` ja vasta hyväksytyn review'n jälkeen `.ballet/outputs/blueprint-gate-packet.yaml`, joka sitoutuu source SHA:han, artifact-hasheihin, oletuksiin, avoimiin päätöksiin, riskeihin, coverageen ja toteuttamattomiin ulkoisiin toimiin.",
          "nodeStyle": "sol",
          "nodeSize": "large",
          "id": "independent-blueprint-verifier",
          "on": {
            "ready": {
              "action": "terminate",
              "status": "blocked"
            },
            "approved": {
              "action": "goto",
              "target": "blueprint-gate"
            },
            "changes-requested": {
              "action": "retry",
              "target": "source-inventory",
              "policy": {
                "maxAttempts": 3,
                "onExhausted": {
                  "action": "terminate",
                  "status": "blocked"
                },
                "stallDetection": "same-evidence"
              }
            },
            "needs_input": {
              "action": "goto",
              "target": "source-decision-gate",
              "input": "signal"
            },
            "blocked": {
              "action": "terminate",
              "status": "blocked"
            },
            "failed": {
              "action": "retry",
              "policy": {
                "maxAttempts": 1,
                "onExhausted": {
                  "action": "terminate",
                  "status": "failed"
                },
                "when": {
                  "failureClassification": "transient"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "type": "agent",
          "agentId": "blueprint-verifier-agent"
        },
        {
          "description": "Hyväksy riippumattomasti verifioitu `.ballet/outputs/blueprint-gate-packet.yaml` juuri sen source SHA:lla ja artifact-hasheilla. Approved-vastauksessa on oltava milestone_id, canonical blueprint_gate_packet -polku, paketin SHA-256 ja source_sha; paketin ulkoiset toimet jäävät not_executed-tilaan.",
          "nodeStyle": "luna",
          "nodeSize": "tiny",
          "id": "blueprint-gate",
          "on": {
            "approved": {
              "action": "goto",
              "target": {
                "loop": "milestone-planning"
              },
              "input": "append-signal"
            },
            "rejected": {
              "action": "retry",
              "target": "source-inventory",
              "input": "append-signal",
              "policy": {
                "maxAttempts": 3,
                "onExhausted": {
                  "action": "terminate",
                  "status": "blocked"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "type": "human"
        },
        {
          "description": "",
          "nodeStyle": "flat",
          "nodeSize": "tiny",
          "id": "completed",
          "type": "completed"
        },
        {
          "description": "",
          "nodeStyle": "flat",
          "nodeSize": "tiny",
          "id": "blocked",
          "type": "blocked"
        },
        {
          "description": "",
          "nodeStyle": "flat",
          "nodeSize": "tiny",
          "id": "failed",
          "type": "failed"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
